# Screenshots Directory Placeholder
This directory contains the screenshots for the Atlas Explorer CRUD application.
Please place your screenshots in this directory with the following filenames:
1. `create_form_top.png` (Form View - Top & Live Card Preview)
2. `create_form_bottom.png` (Form View - Bottom & Section Inputs)
3. `dashboard.png` (Main Dashboard & Analytics Explored List)
4. `search.png` (Filtering & Search Operations list)
5. `update_form.png` (Edit Country Form - Top)
6. `update_form_bottom.png` (Edit Country Form - Scrolled to Bottom)
7. `delete_confirm.png` (Warning Confirm bottom sheet)
8. `delete_success.png` (Successful Deletion Feedback Toast)
